&quot;The Writer&quot; is the fifth track on <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/Ellie+Goulding" class="bbcode_artist">Ellie Goulding</a>'s debut album <a title="Ellie Goulding - Lights" href="http://www.last.fm/music/Ellie+Goulding/Lights" class="bbcode_album">Lights</a>.

 Goulding told Sky Songs: &quot;The Writer is the most personal and emotional song I've written yet. It's about how you'd do anything and change absolutely EVERYTHING about yourself if necessary, just to be noticed by this one person.&quot; 

